html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  body(
    style='margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fdfaf9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif'
  )
    include header.pug

    table(
      width='100%',
      cellpadding='0',
      cellspacing='0',
      border='0',
      style='padding: 20px 0'
    )
      tr
        td(align='center')
          table(
            width='600',
            cellpadding='0',
            cellspacing='0',
            border='0',
            style='border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #ffffff'
          )
            // Greeting
            tr
              td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold'
                )
                  if firstName
                    | Hi #{ firstName },
                  else
                    | Hi there,

            // Main message
            tr
              td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold'
                ) You already logged your first win. That's the hardest step.
                p(style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0') Start your free trial to unlock the full Career Fingerprint experience and keep building your career story.

            // What they unlock
            tr
              td(style='padding: 10px 30px 0 30px')
                p(style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px 0') With a full account you can:
                ul(
                  style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 20px; margin: 5px 0'
                )
                  li Log unlimited achievements and tag them by skill or theme
                  li Generate resume bullet points and interview answers from your wins
                  li Track your growth over time with a career timeline

            // Supporting line
            tr
              td(style='padding: 10px 30px 0 30px')
                p(
                  style='color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 10px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.5'
                ) Your first achievement is already saved. Pick up right where you left off.

            // CTA button
            tr
              td(style='padding: 25px 30px 30px 30px; text-align: center')
                a(
                  href=loginLink,
                  style='background-color: #ff7a8a; color: #000000; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold'
                ) Start your free trial

    include footer.pug
